{
  "stem": "23506.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When he came, it was all those things to the soldatenheim.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then came officers and the one who was in charge of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And his name was Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Gerhard Vurrer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he used to come and said like that, Heil Hitler!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, he really gave a big Heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he showed them around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Jews who were working-- the painters, girls who are washing the floors-- they said, he's such a good man.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't listen to him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He just does it, you know, for, for the game of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he used to say, Heil Hitler, down like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother asked if he can work steady in this place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he was a tall boy, even he was 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- he-- they would have always taken him to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was better to have a place to go and work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that how Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Vurrer came to our-- into our life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because he was bringing food for the-- from the-- for the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They're little, little candies, chocolate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember for my brother, he brought a, he brought underwear, because it was so cold.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one time, my brother was sick or whatever in the evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, and he didn't work the next day and, then in the evening, felt better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, maybe it was 24-hour flu or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he, he went to a concert that a Jewish, Jewish group-- from children in, in, from the ghetto, and a pianist.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We have the best artists in, in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We have a concert pianist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't remember her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She, she was giving concerts on the Polish radio.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
